cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.model

Class UserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.model.UserProfile

  • public class UserProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    UserProfileManager allows for modification of private attributes such found in UserProfile mUsername is the username that the device has specified to author posts with. Default being Guest. mUserAttributesMap is a hashmap used to hold all users allowing for us to know which have up voted and favorite a post mAnswersPostedCount a int representing the number of Answers a user has posted. By Defualt this value is 0. mQuestionPostedCount a int representing the number of Questions a user has posted. By Defualt this value is 0.
    Author:
    Cmput301 Winter 2014 Group 8
